{"tid":1940302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一名警員抄牌期間被一塊從高處自然落下的石頭擊中頭部","createTime":"2020-03-23T16:32:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T17:05:06.000Z","uid":4959,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"6e9a32b02961b1c35f740ea28717e95112509bc3","tid":1940302,"uid":4959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T16:32:47.000Z","msg":"今日(3月23日)晚上，一名警員在屯門良景邨檢控違例泊車期間，被一塊從高處擲下的石頭擊中頭部，流血受傷。人員清醒，現正在醫院接受治療。<br />\n<br />\n初步調查相信，有人從高處擲下石頭，行為極不負責任，被擊中人士可能會嚴重受傷，甚至死亡。警方十分重視案件，目前正在現場展開全面調查。"},{"pid":"f881c6ce3a468ba870794acda2fdb4863d411338","tid":1940302,"uid":36702,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T16:34:43.000Z","msg":"太空隕石 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32a8cceff764ebfbbb90594f5b120f9f5df2aaa5","tid":1940302,"uid":262875,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T16:39:53.000Z","msg":"最緊要<br />\n最好"},{"pid":"595ba916594844f71a5beccdad6828796d7da8c2","tid":1940302,"uid":180814,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T16:43:13.000Z","msg":"嚿石咁高跌落嚟 實好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"022267b269d7300937b91d08540134dd2a95a25b","tid":1940302,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T16:46:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a54a8650bb9a78bc054c8cdc8b834567ee13e1c","tid":1940302,"uid":342786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T16:47:51.000Z","msg":"熱烈地彈琴熱烈地唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab9f42c48eee1cfb8267750caae9b547e7a63e0a","tid":1940302,"uid":248834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T16:50:28.000Z","msg":"又幾準<br />\n咁都中<br />\n部車應該冇事掛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fbb41103dda31e1a